_sText:
Basic BA_JAIL map: JB_PANAMA_PRISON (V1) 

# Actual content:
 - Soccer stadium
 - Swimming Pool
 - Armory (M4A1, M3, AK47, DEAGLE)
 - 14 T Spawns / 10 CT Spawns
 - Cage (with boxes)
 - Medic (Heals 15hp/sec)


# Secret weapons:
 - AWP: Crouch on the ball and then cut it to jump on the walls of the soccer stadium, in a corner you will find an AWP with 10/20 of ammo.
 - USP: Fix the letter "S" of the "BY KODDESCK" in the wall of the soccer stadium then jump, there is normally an USP hidden inside this letter, with 10/120 ammo.
 - DEAGLE: Search between two boxes of the cage, there is a deagle with 7/35 ammo.


Please don't forget it's my first BA_JAIL map. Thanks to post any glitches/improvements.
